      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable daily driver! This car is in honest, fair condition and is perfect for anyone who values a strong engine and steady performance. While it shows some character through its age and expected wear, it remains a functional and hardworking vehicle that's ready for many more miles. If you're looking for a practical ride that gets the job done without the premium price tag, this is the one for you!",
