    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional and honest daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the roof and hood, and minor dings consistent with regular use over the years. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays typical wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, it has been maintained to remain reliable, though it lacks the pristine feel of a newer or garage-kept model. It\u2019s a solid, straightforward car that gets the job done without any pretenses.",
