    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, making it an ideal candidate for a dedicated project or for salvaging parts. The engine requires significant work to run reliably, the transmission is showing signs of failure, and there is visible rust damage on several body panels along with a heavily worn interior. It is not currently roadworthy and will require a trailer for transport, but it could be a valuable find for a mechanic or restorer.",
